name: Wood Maze Deluxe
description:
Wood Maze Deluxe will test your speed, dexterity and agility.

Complete each maze as fast as you can without dropping your marble in a wood hole.

This game offers 6 different mazes and a selection of 24 marbles to customize your experience.

See how you rank in our leaderboards. The game offers 1 leaderboard per Maze.


NB: we have many other great games in the App Store.
